'''''Bernd Niesecke'''''  is a [[Germans|German]] [[rower]], who competed for the ''[[SC Dynamo Potsdam]]''/ ''[[Sportvereinigung (SV) Dynamo]]''. He won the medals at the international rowing competitions.
